{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d1331eeaf4","title":"关于越南奠边府作战应注意事项致彭德怀、黄克诚电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f916e5e4c","index":0,"year":1955,"month":4,"day":28,"articleId":"d1331eeaf4"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"c536537d0b","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长。黄克诚，当时任国防部副部长、中国人民解放军副总参谋长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"10fed62ec0","type":"title","text":"关于越南尊边府作战应注意事项致彭德怀、黄克诚电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4"},{"id":"c536537d0b","type":"paragraph","text":"彭德怀、黄克诚同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4"},{"id":"ffb037bd5f","type":"paragraph","text":"目前越南最大可能发生的危险，似乎不在莫边府以南，而在我军的后方交通线。如敌以两个伞兵营降落在我后方交通线上最抗要的地点，筑堡据守起来，整个交通将为之切断，如我军不能迅速好灭此故，矿日持久，奠边府我军即有被追撤退之可能。军委去电已估计到敌有袭占交通线可能，但强调不够，并以之与琅勃拉邦方向并列。请你们再加考虑，叫越方迅调必要兵力位于适当地区，专门对付此种意外事变，以免莫边府作战功亏一赞。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4"},{"id":"cca6185352","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4"},{"id":"82a213978f","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4"}],"page":{"id":"0467f9e85d","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"d1331eeaf4","start":41,"end":41}}}},"__N_SSG":true}